CURRENT STATUS: 
<bibRefCitation id="845B4B47FE49FE2F5942FB2DFD0965C2" author="Menzel, F. &amp; Mohrig, W." box="[348,698,1184,1211]" pageId="388" pageNumber="389" pagination="1 - 761" refId="ref359551" refString="Menzel, F. &amp; Mohrig, W. (2000) Revision der palaarktischen Trauermucken (Diptera: Sciaridae). Studia Dipterologica, Supplement, 6, 1 - 761." type="journal article" year="2000">Menzel &amp; Mohrig (2000: 601)</bibRefCitation>
